cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SE

The paper discusses the integration of Cyber-Physical Systems (CPSs) with the Internet of Things (IoT), which involves aspects of systems engineering (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of Game Theory (cs.AI) for modelling and programming (cs.SE) of resilient CPSs. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SY, followed by cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.AI, and cs.SE.
